19#include "BitMatrix.h"
20#include "Quadrilateral.h"
21
22#include <utility>
23
24namespace ZXing {
25
26/**
27* Encapsulates the result of detecting a barcode in an image. This includes the raw
28* matrix of black/white pixels corresponding to the barcode and the position of the code
29* in the input image.
30*/
31class DetectorResult
32{
33 BitMatrix _bits;
34 QuadrilateralI _position;
35
36 DetectorResult(const DetectorResult&) = delete;
37 DetectorResult& operator=(const DetectorResult&) = delete;
38
39public:
40 DetectorResult() = default;
41 DetectorResult(DetectorResult&&) = default;
42 DetectorResult& operator=(DetectorResult&&) = default;
43
44 DetectorResult(BitMatrix&& bits, QuadrilateralI&& position)
45 : _bits(std::move(bits)), _position(std::move(position))
46 {}
47
48 const BitMatrix& bits() const & { return _bits; }
49 BitMatrix&& bits() && { return std::move(_bits); }
50 const QuadrilateralI& position() const & { return _position; }
51 QuadrilateralI&& position() && { return std::move(_position); }
52
53 bool isValid() const { return !_bits.empty(); }
54};
55
56} // ZXing
